title: Dragons Den CA - Season 1-12
description:
Dragons' Den is an internationally franchised reality television program which began in Japan. The Canadian show debuted on October 3, 2006. It is broadcast on the CBC Television Network and is hosted by Dianne Buckner. Aspiring Canadian entrepreneurs pitch business and investment ideas to a panel of five venture capitalists (called 'Dragons') in the hope of securing business financing and partnerships.

This is an updated version of my previous torrent which covered the first eleven seasons of Dragons' Den Canada. Obviously, I have added season twelve, but I have also cleaned up the titles of all the video files from the first eleven seasons. Beyond that, I recently discovered that there were many special episodes, especially in seasons 10-12. Therefore, I have further improved upon my previous torrent by revealing which episodes were specials (by printing the name of each special after its 'season + episode' identifier).

Most of the videos here are approximately 480p resolution. A couple are 720p, but some are 360p or worse, especially the older episodes. This is because I did not download the older videos until months or years after the episodes were broadcast. I did the best I could under the circumstances, but at least all the episodes are here! Enjoy!!
